<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Zhao Sheng Wins Men's Floor Exercise Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CATANIA, Sicily, August 24 (Xinhua) -- Zhao Sheng of China took the
men's floor exercise title at the 19th World Universiade on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Zhao, the runner-up in the men's all-around event, collected 9.45
points for the title. Ion Silviu Sucio of Romania and Seong Min Cho
of South Korea tied for the silver medal at 9.300 points each.
</P>
</TEXT>
