<DOCNO> XIE19970825.0036 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-08-25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Italy Advance with 4-0 Victory over Netherlands </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CATANIA, Sicily, August 24 (Xinhua) -- Hosts Italy powered into the
semi-finals of the Universiade soccer tournament after scoring a 4-0
victory over the Netherlands at Borsellino on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The Italians, who got the signal of advance only at the last minute
of the group competitions, played much better today.
</P>
<P>
Yet they could not find a quick way of scoring and had to wait
until the 44th minute of the first half.
</P>
<P>
Alessandro Ambrosi finally opened the scoring gate for the Italians
with a thundering shot which beat the Dutch goal-keeper.
</P>
<P>
The second half became merely a scoring practice for the Italians
as Ambrosi completed his hat-trick by scoring two more goals at the
60th and 76th minutes respectively.
</P>
<P>
Edoardo Gorini completed the 4-0 victory for the host team with a
goal at the 85th minute. 
</P>
</TEXT>
