<HEADLINE> Taiwan "Referendum" Attempt Refuted (6) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Compatriots across the Taiwan Straits are closely related by
blood, and we understand and respect the desire of Taiwan people
for the development of democratic politics, the article says.
</P>
<P>
We believe that the Taiwan people with patriotic tradition will
surely see through the fraud of separation under the cloak of
democracy, and will resist the adverse current of separation, it
says.
</P>
<P>
The article points out that reunifying the country according to
the principle of "one country, two systems" will promote the
integration of sovereignty and territory, and will protect the
fundamental interests of the people on Taiwan. This, it continues,
will prevent them from suffering losses, and enable them to enjoy
the internationally recognized dignity and glory of their
motherland.
</P>
<P>
The return of Hong Kong and the practice of "one country, two
systems" have provided a model for peaceful reunification of the
motherland, the article says.
</P>
<P>
The reunification of China and the revitalization of the
Chinese nation as a whole is an irresistible historical trend, it
says, adding that However, a few people on Taiwan Island who
preach an independent Taiwan are running counter to the trend, and
will in the end lose all their standing and destroy their
reputations. 
