technologies and to stimulate the process for transforming
scientific and technological results into realistic productivity
in order to constantly resolve important and key problems emerging
in economic construction, Jiang said, adding that efforts should
also center on promoting fundamental changes in the economic
system and modes of economic growth.
</P>
<P>
According to Jiang, late Chinese leader Deng Xiaoping stressed
that China should assume its due place in the world's high-tech
sector, and that our generation should strive to realize the
objective which will have far-reaching significance.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said the country should pool necessary manpower,
financial strength and material resources to develop new high
technology which will be of strategic importance to China's
economic and social development in the 21st century.
</P>
<P>
He noted that China should learn advanced technology from
foreign countries and should at the same time form and develop the
country's own superiorities in science and technology.
</P>
<P>
