and Technology Leading Group, sponsored the third session of the
leading group this June. Participants in the session heard the
reports given by State Science and Technology Commission and State
Planning Commission on the development of the key basic scientific
research, on new and high-tech industries, and on the
implementation of the state's important scientific projects.
