Dawn-to-Dusk general strike called by Bangladesh's opposition
parties in protest against the fuel price hike, said informed
sources.
</P>
<P>
Police sources said the major incidents took place in front of
the National Press Club this afternoon while police lobbed several
rounds of teargas shells to disperse the opposition
activists. (Bangladesh-Strike)
</P>
